>Description:</h5><p>获取系统总内存量（MB）。Gets the total amount of system memory in megabytes for system capacity planning.</p>\n<h5>Returns:</h5><p>总内存（MB）。Total memory in MB</p>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// System specifications</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">totalMemMB</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">totalmem</span>();\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span>Total system memory: ${<span class=\"pl-smi\">totalMemMB</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">toFixed</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">2</span>)} MB<span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Memory-based configuration</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">maxWorkers</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Math</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">floor</span>(<span class=\"pl-en\">totalmem</span>() <span class=\"pl-k\">/</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">1024</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// 1 worker per GB</span>\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span>Configuring ${<span class=\"pl-smi\">maxWorkers</span>} workers based on ${<span class=\"pl-smi\">totalMemMB</span>} MB RAM<span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Since:</h5><p>1.0.0</p>\n<h5>See:</h5><ul>\n<li><a href=\"2190\">freemem</a> - Get free system memory</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/os.html#os_os_totalmem\">https://nodejs.org/api/os.html#os_os_totalmem</a> - Node.js os.totalmem() documentation</li>\n</ul>\n"},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/system/os.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/node-utils/src/system/os.ts","line":194,"character":0,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/ut